OL,6,FAlliance Party leader and Justice
OL,7,FMinister Naomi Long said: "Sir Kenneth
OL,8,Fhad a distinguished career in public
OL,9,Fservice over many years and in many
OL,10,Froles.
OL,12,F"He and his wife were personally
OL,13,Ftargeted in the Troubles, when their
OL,14,Fhome was attacked by an IRA bomb, but
OL,15,Fhe did not allow it to deter him from
OL,16,Fhis enduring commitment to public
OL,17,Fservice.
